===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Colress (Masters)}}
Colress, in his {{B2W2}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Klinklang}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Colress became a playable sync pair on November 17, 2022.

Colress first appeared as an NPC during the [[Unova]] chapter of the [[villain arc]]. Colress has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the villain arc.

